functionDecorators.name: changeBuyingTokenFee
functionDecorators.description: Update the buying token fee for this contract defaults at 20.00% of taxFee, It can be set on only by YZY governance. Note contract owner is meant to be a governance contract allowing YZY governance consensus.

functionDecorators.name: changeBuyingTokenRewardPeriod
functionDecorators.description: Change value of reward period. Call by only Governance.

functionDecorators.name: changeBuyingWBTCTokenFee
functionDecorators.description: Update the buying WBTC token fee for this contract defaults at 30.00% of buyingTokenFee Note contract owner is meant to be a governance contract allowing YZY governance consensus.

functionDecorators.name: changeBuyingWETHTokenFee
functionDecorators.description: Update the buying WETH token fee for this contract defaults at 20.00% of buyingTokenFee Note contract owner is meant to be a governance contract allowing YZY governance consensus.

functionDecorators.name: changeBuyingYFITokenFee
functionDecorators.description: Update the buying YFI token fee for this contract defaults at 50.00% of buyingTokenFee Note contract owner is meant to be a governance contract allowing YZY governance consensus.

functionDecorators.name: changeDevFee
functionDecorators.description: Update the dev fee for this contract defaults at 4.00% of taxFee, It can be set on only by YZY governance. Note contract owner is meant to be a governance contract allowing YZY governance consensus.

functionDecorators.name: changeDevFeeReciever
functionDecorators.description: Update dev address by the previous dev. Note onlyOwner functions are meant for the governance contract allowing YZY governance token holders to do this functions.

functionDecorators.name: changeRewardPeriod
functionDecorators.description: Change value of reward period. Call by only Governance.

functionDecorators.name: changeTreasuryFee
functionDecorators.description: Update the treasury fee for this contract defaults at 76.00% of taxFee, It can be set on only by YZY governance. Note contract owner is meant to be a governance contract allowing YZY governance consensus.
